Standing high on a bluff overlooking the mighty St. Lawrence River, Fairmont Le Château Frontenac is not merely a hotel located in the heart of Old Québec - it is the heart of it. At Fairmont Le Château Frontenac, guests are guaranteed a memorable and inspiring stay in one of the most beautiful cities in the world with easy walking access to all of the wonderful sites and experiences that Old Québec has to offer.

Reviews

Reviews summary
This summary was created by AI, based on recent reviews.
Powered by AI
Nestled in Old Quebec, Fairmont Le Château Frontenac offers a blend of historic elegance and luxury, though the charm may not extend to all rooms, with some criticized as dated. Its prime location is unanimously lauded, providing stunning views and proximity to attractions. While the hotel's cleanliness receives high marks, opinions on amenities are divided, with some guests disappointed by limited access and crowded spaces. Service quality varies, and despite the professional staff, instances of slow service have been noted. Many guests consider the pricing steep for what is offered.
